    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Somniora is a horror-puzzle game.</strong> Get ready to delve into the adventure of our character, who is trapped amidst strange dreams, while searching for answers to the questions lurking in their subconscious.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235130/extras/5c2dc6a6681c845aa00e45500c239337.poster.avif?t=1772039091\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235130/extras/5c2dc6a6681c845aa00e45500c239337.webm?t=1772039091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235130/extras/5c2dc6a6681c845aa00e45500c239337.mp4?t=1772039091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i><strong>Amara</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Amara is a character struggling with sleep problems and the weight of her past. She finds herself in a repeating dark dream world and must keep moving forward to escape it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235130/extras/3ff03da4162997acc03104c43145da05.poster.avif?t=1772039091\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235130/extras/3ff03da4162997acc03104c43145da05.webm?t=1772039091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235130/extras/3ff03da4162997acc03104c43145da05.mp4?t=1772039091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i><strong>Puzzle</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progression in Somniora is supported by environmental puzzles. The player must carefully observe their surroundings, combine clues, and unlock new areas.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235130/extras/b177912c87746d048ff65e1264fc53b4.poster.avif?t=1772039091\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235130/extras/b177912c87746d048ff65e1264fc53b4.webm?t=1772039091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235130/extras/b177912c87746d048ff65e1264fc53b4.mp4?t=1772039091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i><strong>The Big Day</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the story progresses, a helping hand reaches out to our character, who is trying to understand what is happening here, and speaks of an approaching revolution. If Amara carries out this revolution, she will start “The Big Day” on the other side.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235130/extras/2eecae1f56e65ea5e07ba460d44039c8.poster.avif?t=1772039091\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235130/extras/2eecae1f56e65ea5e07ba460d44039c8.webm?t=1772039091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235130/extras/2eecae1f56e65ea5e07ba460d44039c8.mp4?t=1772039091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i><strong>Mechanics</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player will have access to multiple tools to progress through the dream. Since Amara cannot control her dream, using these tools at the right time and in the right place is very important for progression throughout the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235130/extras/4f02adf4eb67649822b816a902882cda.poster.avif?t=1772039091\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235130/extras/4f02adf4eb67649822b816a902882cda.webm?t=1772039091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235130/extras/4f02adf4eb67649822b816a902882cda.mp4?t=1772039091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i><strong>Traumas</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do your best to move forward in this unknown place, but you will not be alone on this side. Amara’s deepest traumas will be there to turn this dream into a real nightmare.</p>",
